<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.10.8">
<l>pūṅku runtocit tāṉaikāyn tari mācce kuttaṭi yēṉaiyā ḷukan</l>
<l>tīṅkeṉ ṉuḷpukun tāṉimai yōrkaḷtam perumāṉ</l>
<l>tūṅku taṇpala viṉkaṉi toku vāḻai yiṉkaṉi yoṭumāṅ kaṉi</l>
<l>tēṅku taṇpuṉal cūḻtiruk kōṭṭiyū rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who entered here in my heart, delighting in accepting me [his] servant,</l>
<l>Having broken the budding lime tree, killed the elephant,</l>
<l rend="indent">and destroyed a horse,</l>
<l>The lord of the unblinking [celestials] is the one in Tirukkōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounded by cool waters</l>
<l>Teeming with mangoes, clusters of banana fruit, and dangling cool jackfruit.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
